Package nameExtractor

package nameExtractor
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    MainClass
    Main entry point for the Name Extractor application.
    MavenUtils
    Utility class providing methods for handling Maven-related file operations, including path construction, temporary copies for compilation, and compiling Java source files while preserving the original file.
    ParsingUtils
    Utility class providing methods to parse Java source files, configure symbol solving, and discover package directories for a project.
    Templates
    Utility class to check if a list of statement types matches predefined templates.
    Utils
    General utility methods for file handling, directory management, and analyzing Java statements using JavaParser.
    Visitors
    Utility class containing various JavaParser visitors to collect specific AST elements.
    Visitors.CollectAssignments
    Visitor to collect variable assignments.
    Visitors.CollectForEachStmt
    Visitor to collect all enhanced for-each loops (ForEachStmt) in a compilation unit or block.
    Visitors.CollectForStmt
    Visitor to collect all traditional for-loops (ForStmt) in a compilation unit or block.
    Visitors.CollectNames
    Visitor to collect all variable references (NameExpr) in a block or statement.
    Visitors.CollectSimpleNames
    Visitor to collect all simple identifiers (SimpleName) in the AST.
    Visitors.CollectUnary
    Visitor to collect variables involved in unary expressions.
    Visitors.CollectVariable
    Visitor to collect variable names from variable declarations.
